publisher			Steven Colling							
publish_time	 2016年2月17日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							In Brushwood Buddies, an unusual puzzle game, adorable creatures will enlist your help to craft various items as they journey through forests, grasslands, and villages! Discover tons of recipes, and find clever ways to manage inventory space and resources while keeping your buddies happy. Be prepared for a variety of puzzles throughout the whole campaign!Challenge modes allow experienced players to earn their rank on the Steam leaderboards and compete against players worldwide. You can even create and share puzzles with your own items and recipes!About the DeveloperMy name is Steven Colling and I'm a solo developer from Germany. Brushwood Buddies is my first Steam release and I hope you enjoy it!						
